Wandering Jew's Chronicle

Original Source

These transcriptions and their accompanying images include at least one copy of all original versions of the Wandering Jew's Chronicle known to the editor at the time of publication, not including later reprints. A full description of the publishing history of the ballad and a bibliography of all currently located copies is given on the project website. Sources and other files are available at https://github.com/gbergel/WJC.
